{"tid":231692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民熱話：爆肌男慳車費？掹巴士邊踩Roller","createTime":"2017-05-06T08:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T09:29:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69b48ba8b3f1f59aecff0d4d5b22642596dbbeb7","tid":231692,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170506/photo/bkn-20170506104254559-0506_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170506145633\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170506%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170506104254559-0506_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170506145633&h=6a155ee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">外籍男掹巴士邊搭順風車的奇招慳交通費？抑或純粹貪玩。(fb柏斯敦巴士台plaxtonl's Bus Page圖片)</span><br />\n1/2<br />\n香港的交通費高昂，雖然港鐵和九巴分別推出回贈或折扣優惠，但未必人人享受到，唔知喺咪因為咁，有人就想出掹巴士邊搭順風車的奇招慳交通費？定純粹貪玩而已。<br />\n<br />\n近日有facebook群組「柏斯敦巴士台plaxtonl's Bus Page」轉載兩張照片。其中一張照片見一名身型健碩、赤裸上身的疑似外籍人士，身穿牛仔褲、腳踩滾軸溜冰鞋，在中環(交易廣場)巴士總站用手扶住巴士車尾，擺姿勢拍照；另一張則該爆肌外籍男用手指掹住似在行駛中巴士車尾，像是搭順風車般「尾隨」巴士碌出馬路。有人質疑大隻佬「連車錢都唔肯俾(畀)，要咁樣搭順風車」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民對照片都議論紛紛，有人笑稱其實爆肌男正在推巴士享受廢氣，建議他下次試推輕鐵和電車，亦有好心地的網民，就關心巴士車尾的散熱位會否過熱。當然亦有網民斥爆肌男罔顧自身和其他道路使用者安全，因巴士若急煞停，後果不堪設想。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nKason Au：另外想問佢點過隧道。。。<br />\n<br />\nHo Nam Man：外國好興咁樣做<br />\n<br />\nSamuel W Tc：真係富.貴.險.中.求.<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170506/bkn-20170506104254559-0506_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170506%2Fbkn-20170506104254559-0506_00822_001.html&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2b37d9d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170506/bkn-20170506104254559-0506_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"142803f3eea1341dbce055a86ed62d41c5bc4ae9","tid":231692,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"用碌鳩勾住死氣喉"},{"pid":"95ee9aea62e85684e1cac5ca1c1c1f2a09cac74c","tid":231692,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4b264ac30b8281d63f5b42a24ff2a79077e98e","tid":231692,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a6e68003a7b2d340e325583f5b4d78f8055ab9a","tid":231692,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"三十歲人仲要依賴交通工具"},{"pid":"970a58b8af27403e189238d9f84588cfd61f777f","tid":231692,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"香港勁秋"}]}